We're building a Moon Base! 

@NASAMoonBase will serve as a habitat where astronauts live and work during long-term science missions.

Join us at 2pm ET on Tuesday, May 26, for a live news event where we’ll share updates on our lunar exploration plans: https://www.nasa.gov/news-release/nasa-to-provide-update-on-moon-base-strategy-missions/?utm_source=TWITTER&utm_medium=NASA&utm_campaign=NASASocial&linkId=945779084
